snippet.title: SRB2 Heroes (Download now)
snippet.description:
Hey all! This is my third attemp at making a Sonic Heroes mod. Yep, third. First one was cancelled (and was really bad by the way). Second one was complete but got deleted when my computer broke, so I never had the chance to upload it. And third one... here it is!

Download at SRB2 forum: http://mb.srb2.org/showthread.php?goto=newpost&t=40876

Not recomended for SRB2 Community Build since dash panels work differently.
Have fun and tell me if you like it :D
